HEADWORD: Gazon
<hw>Ga*zon"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>gazon</ets>
turf, fr. OHG. <ets>waso</ets>, G. <ets>wasen</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Fort.)</fld> <def>One of the pieces of sod used to line or cover
parapets and the faces of earthworks.</def>⟦br⟧
